---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure — CryptoBonusWorld"
  description="Full affiliate disclosure for CryptoBonusWorld.com. How we earn compensation and how it affects our content."
  canonical="/affiliate-disclosure/"
>
  <div class="container">
    <Breadcrumbs crumbs={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Affiliate Disclosure' },
    ]} />
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="prose">
      <h2>How We Earn</h2>
      <p>CryptoBonusWorld.com is an affiliate website. We earn compensation when users register on crypto exchanges through affiliate or referral links on this website. Compensation may be in the form of:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Revenue share (RevShare) — a percentage of trading fees generated by referred users.</li>
        <li>Cost-per-acquisition (CPA) — a fixed payment per qualifying registration, KYC completion or first deposit.</li>
        <li>Hybrid arrangements combining RevShare and CPA.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How This Affects Our Content</h2>
      <p>Our affiliate relationships may influence:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Which exchanges are featured on this website.</li>
        <li>The order in which exchanges appear in comparison tables.</li>
        <li>The prominence given to specific bonus offers.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Our affiliate relationships do NOT affect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>The factual accuracy of bonus data we publish.</li>
        <li>Our editorial rating methodology.</li>
        <li>Our risk disclosures or compliance requirements.</li>
        <li>Our decision to include accurate cons and conditions for each exchange.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Identifying Affiliate Links</h2>
      <p>All "Claim Bonus" and exchange registration buttons on CryptoBonusWorld link to exchanges through affiliate tracking links. These links are clearly labeled as external links and marked with rel="nofollow sponsored" attributes.</p>

      <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
      <p>We only list exchanges we believe to be reputable. We will not promote exchanges with documented fraud, widespread user complaints about fund withdrawal, or significant regulatory violations. We include risk warnings, conditions and cons for every exchange regardless of our affiliate relationship.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about our affiliate relationships, please <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.</p>

      <p><em>Last updated: May 2026</em></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
